  "description": "The Retcher is a Tediore Seraph shotgun from Pirate's Booty. It fires corrosive orbs in a low arc, which makes landing shots at close range easier but sharply limits reach. Unlike E-tech Splatguns it only spends 1 ammo per shot, so it keeps a healthier magazine and better damage per ammo, but it also misses out on the boosted status chance those guns get.\n\nReloading throws the gun as a grenade. It also lobs two small child grenades high upwards; they detonate on contact and are usually awkward to use indoors. Despite their green look, the child blasts deal explosive damage.",
